text: Terry Waxman (born December 28, 1956) is an American politician who has served in the West Virginia House of Delegates from the 48th district since 2018. She previously served in the West Virginia House of Delegates from 2014 to 2016. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the West Virginia House of Delegates Category:West Virginia Republicans
